zm_tutorials_afterlife:
Welcome to the AFTERLIFE ARCADE!

Here you can earn a SOUL TOKEN by playing the games in the arcade and filling the SOUL METER at the bottom of the screen. You can also spectate the other players in your game if you want to keep your eye on the action. With an earned SOUL TOKEN, you can instantly revive yourself and rejoin the fight by exiting the SELF REVIVE DOOR.
zm_tutorials_atm: Need a rainy day fund?  Deposit cash into the ATM for park visitors to withdraw. Deposits and withdrawals are handled in $1000 increments and can be shared between all visitors.
zm_tutorials_door_buy: Throughout Spaceland you will find doors that block your entrance into some locations of the park. For a small fee you can purchase your way past these barricades and gain access to more areas of the park. See if you can explore the entire park!
zm_tutorials_fortune_deck: Now that your Fate and Fortune Meter is full you can use one of the cards in your deck.  When you run out of cards, visit one of the Fortune Tellers to replenish your deck.
zm_tutorials_lost_and_found: Dead and lost your weapons? No worries. When playing with others, return to the LOST & FOUND located at the park’s main entrance to recover your weapons. Don’t waste too much time though. The park will only hold your stuff for a limited time.
zm_tutorials_magic_wheel: See that shaft of light in the sky? The MAGIC WHEEL awards players a random weapon for a small fee. Some of the weapons in the MAGIC WHEEL cannot be found anywhere else within Spaceland. Watch out though, sometimes the wheel will only award you a consolation prize. Find the MAGIC WHEEL, give it a spin and press your luck!
zm_tutorials_neil:
Hey, thanks for putting N31L back together!

Now that he’s back, N31L is looking for some worthy park goers to show they have the right stuff to save Spaceland. Try completing the N31L challenges that appear in the top left of the screen and he just might return the favor.  Good luck!
zm_tutorials_pack_a_punch: Upgrading your weapons in zombies is crucial to your survival in later scenes. Through the elusive Pack A Punch machine you can further increase the power of your weapons for a fee. Most weapons can be upgraded multiple times and even gain new abilities.
zm_tutorials_perks: Sprinkled throughout Spaceland are 10 PERK stations that, for a fee, can greatly expand your capabilities. You can carry up to 5 PERKS at a time and can mix and match which you pair up. Be careful though, if you go down you will lose all of your PERKS and have to repurchase them!
zm_tutorials_power_ups: Zombies will occasionally drop POWER UPS after being killed that offer insane temporary upgrades for the entire team. Simply walk into a POWER UP to collect it and it activates immediately. Don't wait too long though, POWER UPS time out after a short period of time so collect them as soon as you can or you might miss out!
zm_tutorials_power_switches: Throughout Spaceland there are POWER SWITCHES that can be turned on that activate key things within the park like PERK stations and TRAPS. POWER SWITCHES are free to activate and permanently activate POWER for their given area. Try to find all of the POWER SWITCHES and completely restore power to Spaceland.
zm_tutorials_pillage: When zombies are killed they will occasionally drop bags on the ground. The bags contain random items like ammo clips, cash and more! Try searching the dropped bags to see what the zombies left behind for you.
zm_tutorials_quests: Spaceland features a set of QUESTS that can be completed by recovering specific items spread out and hidden within the park. When a QUEST item is recovered it will appear in your inventory screen [{togglescores}]. Recovering these QUEST items puts you one step closer to solving the mysteries of Spaceland and hopefully one step closer to escaping Willard Wyler's epic film.
zm_tutorials_scenes: In zombies players are pitted against wave after wave of zombies. Each SCENE contains a set number of zombies to defeat. When all of the zombies are killed, the SCENE ends and the next one begins. Watch out though, the zombies get craftier and more powerful with every SCENE.
zm_tutorials_souvenir_coins: SOUVENIR COINS can be obtained by killing zombies and can be traded in for goodies at one of the many SOUVENIR STATIONS located in and around Spaceland. If you already have a SOUVENIR COIN you can swap to another.
zm_tutorials_souvenir_stations: SOUVENIR STATIONS can craft special Spaceland goodies. By depositing 3 SOUVENIR COINS into a station, players are awarded a SOUVENIR. Try to mix and match formulas to see all of the SOUVENIRS you can earn!
zm_tutorials_team_door_buy: Some of the doors within Spaceland can be opened with team work. Players can take turns depositing money into the door to open it so that no one player is saddled with the cost burden. Deposit increments are $1000 per player.
zm_tutorials_tickets: TICKETS can be earned by playing games within the park like Octonian Hunter, killing zombies with TRAPS and recovered in dropped PILLAGE bags. TICKETS can be exchanged at one of the TICKET PRIZE BOOTHS located around Spaceland. Keep an eye out for very special items that can only be purchased with TICKETS.
zm_tutorials_traps: Throughout Spaceland parts of the park have been altered into traps that can kill lots of zombies and protect players when things get tough. TRAPS cost a small fee and can earn players valuable Spaceland park TICKETS for every kill they gain the player.
zm_tutorials_window_boarding: Barricades have been set up to keep the zombies out. The problem is the zombies keep tearing the WINDOW BOARDS down. If you put the boards back up, you can keep zombies out of the play space longer and gain some cash for each board you restore. Try to keep Spaceland secure and yourself safe!
zm_tutorials_zombie_health: Every SCENE the zombie capabilities will increase. They will move faster, do more damage and make more aggressive attempts at eating your brains. The later the SCENE, the more powerful your zombie adversaries will be.  Be sure to aim for the head, as headshots do a lot more damage!
zm_tutorials_craftable: There are a variety of SOUVENIRS available from using different combinations of SOUVENIR COINS.  To pull out your SOUVENIR press [{+actionslot 3}] and then press [{+attack}] to place it.
zm_tutorials_fortune_card_machine: There are Fortune Tellers throughout Spaceland, eager and willing to restock your Fate and Fortune Cards...for a fee of course.
zm_tutorials_wall_buy: There are a variety of weapons available for purchase in Spaceland. If you come across a weapon you are already in possession of, you can buy ammo at a discount. You can only carry two weapons at a time without the Mule Munchies perk candy.

cp_loadout_wall_desc: Laser Walls can be connected to provide a perimeter defense from most enemy types.
cp_loadout_sniper_tower_desc: The Sniper Tower allows for a heightened vantage point, perfect for picking off enemies at a distance.
cp_loadout_armordepot_desc: The Armor Regen Field will slowly regenerate the player's armor if they are within it's range.
cp_loadout_trophy_desc: The Iron Dome protects against projectile attacks by nullifying them when they are within range.
cp_loadout_antiair_desc: The Anti-Air Missile Launching System attacks airborne enemies with a barrage of missiles.
cp_loadout_imf_desc: The I.M.F. targets nearby enemies and fires an explosive charge that will detonate on contact.
cp_loadout_lightning_tower_desc: The Lightning Tower arcs a powerful electric bolt at nearby enemies.  Those who don't get killed will get stunned in their tracks.
cp_loadout_phalanx_desc: Phalanxes are powerful automated machine gun turrets that can mow down enemies.
cp_loadout_generator_desc: These Generators provide additional power to the grid and enabling more defenses to be able to be deployed.
cp_loadout_accelerator_desc: The Extractor Accelerator hastens the extraction process by siphoning the grid's power and feeding it back into the Extractor.
cp_loadout_medusa_bomb_desc: The Medusa Device absorbs the souls of fallen enemies. When the Medusa has filled completely it can be detonated, causing a massive destructive shockwave that will eliminate all enemies.
cp_loadout_weapondepot_desc: The Weapon Upgrade Module allows allies to upgrade their current primary weapon.  Multiple levels of upgrades are available.
cp_loadout_perk_robotics_desc:
The Robotics Expert believes the answer to everything can be found in AI. They rely solely on the companions they've built to survive.

[{+smoke}] ^3Kinetic Pulse [{+frag}] Repulsor^7

[{+gostand}] ^2Double Jump^7

cp_loadout_perk_gunslinger_desc:
The Gunslinger cannot sit still. They run around with akimbo pistols and attempt to wear down the opposition.

aliens_perk_pistol_magnum_desc_3: Hip Fire two pistols for twice the firepower and twice the ammo capacity.

See enemies through walls.
Increased sprint endurance.
Regenerate health faster.
Lasts 45 sec.
aliens_team_adrenaline_desc_4: Increases the booster's duration by 3x and adds increased sprint endurance.
aliens_soldier_type_desc:
What kind of soldier will you be going into this fight?

Choose between eight types of soldiers: a tank, a weapon specialist, a medic, an engineer, a robotics expert, a demolitions expert, a gunslinger, and a hybrid.

Tip: When partying up, try having different types of soldiers on your team.
aliens_pistol_type_desc:
Your pistol is there with you from the beginning and can never leave your side.

The pistol can be upgraded using skill points.  Upgrades will boost the damage, ammo capacity, and even allow you to hold two pistols at once, akimbo style.

Tip: Upgrade the pistol enough so you can carry two primary weapons alongside it.
aliens_ammo_type_desc:
Ammo is in short supply and, therefore, extremely valuable.

Throw down an ammo cache for the entire team to resupply from.  Additional ammo types such as stun, incendiary, explosive and armor piercing will give your team the extra firepower they need to finish the job.
aliens_team_support_desc:
Provide supplies for the team by deploying a cache for everyone to restock from.

Supplies such as armor, explosives, and boosters will benefit the entire team. Use your skill points in game to further increase the duration and effectiveness of the supplies.

Tip: Encourage teammates to each use a different supply as their benefits will compound.
aliens_strike_package_desc:
The ultimate in firepower, strike packages are perfect for defense or for raining pain.

They may cost a bit more, but strike packages are well worth it.  A fully levelled up strike package can do serious damage.

Tip: Experiment with different options, and don't forget to level them up.
aliens_equalizer_desc:
The Equalizers provide personal, heavy firepower.

Generally hand-held weapons, these can be purchased in a pinch, regardless of the total ammo at hand.

Tip: Choose an Equalizer based on playing style.  If you run a lot, try putting the Riot Shield on your back by changing weapons.
aliens_nerf_desc:
Relics are earned by passing Rank 30.  They increase the difficulty and, thus, enhance the score.

Each time the player passes Rank 30 they get the privilege of using an additional Relic.  Up to five Relics can be used at once.  The more Relics used, the higher the scoring bonus received.

vidsubtitles_hereandnowwe: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7Here and now, we will eradicate the authority and influence of the Earth!
vidsubtitles_todaythefrontem: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7Today, the Front embarks on a conquest.
vidsubtitles_hadtheyhappened: "Had they happened to be in the reach of predatory human hands."
vidsubtitles_thesunthemoonandthe: ^7"The sun, the moon and the stars would have disappeared long ago..."
vidsubtitles_ourexpertstellus: ^2Reporter: ^7Our experts tell us that the vacuum of space should render the compound inert, but without the exact makeup of the agent, they cannot say this with complete certainty.
vidsubtitles_thehealthorganization: ^2Reporter: ^7The Health Organization announced that relief efforts for off-world colonies are underway.
vidsubtitles_despitethesuccessr: ^2Reporter: ^7Despite the success, reports indicate that the chemical agent was not completely contained.
vidsubtitles_severaltimesbutwhen: ^2Salter: ^7Several times. But, when the major retired he signed the petition for my Distinguished Flying Cross so, hey, I guess he got over it.
vidsubtitles_iwasdoingalittlelow: ^2Salter: ^7I was doing a little low flying myself. Apparently it made quite a mess.
vidsubtitles_youbuzzedhishouse: ^2Reyes: ^7You buzzed his house in San Anselmo while his wife was hosting the officers wive’s club formal in the backyard, Salt.
vidsubtitles_oneinthesame: ^2Salter: ^7One in the same. We never got back on track after that.
vidsubtitles_bingosoiseetheguy: ^2Salter: ^7Bingo. So I see the guy the next morning on the way out to the transport, and I say “good morning snake shit”, and he says, “that’s Major snake shit, Lieutenant Salter”.
vidsubtitles_rightbecauseevent: ^2Reyes: ^7Right, 'cause eventually you’re just landing or crashing.
vidsubtitles_anditellhimyoucan: ^2Salter: ^7And I tell him you can only tie the record for flying low.
vidsubtitles_soihearthisguyinabar: ^2Salter: ^7So, I overhear this guy in a bar talking about having the record for flying low, says he can fly under snake shit, so I chime in...
vidsubtitles_youaregoingtohaveto: ^2Salter: ^7You are going to have to edit this.
vidsubtitles_welltokeepthingscop: ^2Reyes: ^7Well, to keep things copacetic, just tell the ‘snake shit’ story.
vidsubtitles_ahmanimgoingtohave: ^2Reyes: ^7Ah, man. I'm going to have to edit this.
vidsubtitles_majorkennywasamajor: ^2Salter: ^7Major Kenny was a major blow hard, and he was full of shit, and his wife was a stuck up broom rider.
vidsubtitles_youhadsomeissues: ^2Reyes: ^7You had some issues with Major Kenny...
vidsubtitles_letstalkalittle: ^2Reyes: ^7Let's talk a little about your disciplinary record.
vidsubtitles_beadvisediwillbe: ^2Salter: ^7Be advised, I will be recording my interview with you as well so, watch your a…tread accordingly, Lieutenant.
vidsubtitles_anofficialunsaannou: ^2Reporter: ^7An official UNSA announcement is expected shortly, but this is already being hailed as a critical blow to the SetDef’s offensive capabilities.
vidsubtitles_oursourcestellusthe: ^2Reporter: ^7Our sources tell us the target was a Settlement Defense Front ship harboring some kind of prototype technology. After a brief skirmish, SATO forces were able to board the vessel and apprehend that prototype.
vidsubtitles_justmomentsagounsa: ^2Reporter: ^7Just moments ago, UNSA forces along with the Navy’s elite SATO teams launched a surprise offensive near the Uranian moon, Miranda.
vidsubtitles_foriwnew5: ^2Reporter: ^7For IW News, this is Gerome Davies.
vidsubtitles_inrelatednewssetdef: ^2Reporter: ^7In related news, SetDef fleet movements continue to impede the flow of off-world resources back to earth. Without those resources, chances severely dwindle for damaged SATO warships to be repaired.
vidsubtitles_accordingtosources: ^2Reporter: ^7According to sources, high-ranking SetDef officials were targeted and eliminated by an elite SCAR team.
vidsubtitles_reportsarenowcomingin: ^2Reporter: ^7Reports are now coming in about a targeted strike by SATO forces on a secret SetDef leadership conference.
vidsubtitles_continuingcoverage: ^2Reporter: ^7Continuing coverage following today’s horrific attack on Geneva.
vidsubtitles_intelsuggeststheirtar: ^2Warlord: ^7Intel suggests their target is a prototype weapon. Your team will extract the prototype and torch the site before SDF can locate it.
vidsubtitles_oneofourweaponsfaci: ^2Warlord: ^7One of our weapons facilities is under attack by the SDF. We believe this is part of an operation, codenamed: RIAH.
vidsubtitles_warlordthisisscar1: ^2Wolf: ^7Warlord this is SCAR-1. Standing by for tasking.
vidsubtitles_itisnotenoughtobreak: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7It is not enough to break free. We will break them!
vidsubtitles_ourworldisjustbegin: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7Our world is just beginning. Theirs is dying!
vidsubtitles_theircitieswillburn: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7Their cities will burn along with the pages of their history.
vidsubtitles_youwillnottakemycarr: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7You will not take my carrier, Captain Reyes! We will all die here. I will detonate this vessel and level your city.
vidsubtitles_youwerealwaysafastle: ^2Raines: ^7You were always a fast learner, Lieutenant.
vidsubtitles_youthinktheyllcancel: ^2Reyes: ^7You think they’ll cancel the fleet week festivities?
vidsubtitles_yourmenarewaitingfor: ^2Salter: ^7Your men are waiting for you, Sergeant. Get'em set. Stand by for orders.
vidsubtitles_youresergeantnowyour: ^2Reyes: ^7You're Sergeant now. You're the commander of the Marines on this ship.
vidsubtitles_youreonashuttlefromm: ^2Ferran: ^7You're on a shuttle from my vessel Tigris. I'm taking you back to Retribution.
vidsubtitles_youreneededonthebrid: ^2Gator: ^7You're needed on the bridge ASAP, sir.
vidsubtitles_youremachoneatsevenh: ^2Griff: ^7Now you're Mach One at seven hundred meters.
vidsubtitles_yourejustamanfromear: ^2Riah: ^7You're just a man from Earth, dying for a lost cause.
vidsubtitles_youregoingtowantanen: ^2Griff: ^7You're going to want an energy weapon, then. Makes quick work of those SetDef bots.
vidsubtitles_yourcrewiswaitingfor: ^2Salter: ^7Your crew is waiting for you, Captain.
vidsubtitles_youllnevermakeitback: ^2Salter: ^7You'll never make it back to the ship. If we wait, they'll fire on us.
vidsubtitles_youlllandatransporto: ^2Raines: ^7You’ll land a transport outside their patrol perimeter with Marines to scout an LZ for reinforcements. Once those troops are on the surface, you'll take out their main fueling tower.
vidsubtitles_youllhavewhatyouneed: ^2Omar: ^7You'll have what you need from me, Lieutenant.
vidsubtitles_yougotthegreenlightt: ^2Reyes: ^7You got the green light to do whatever it takes. Just finish the mission.
vidsubtitles_yougotsomeshoestofil: ^2Omar: ^7You got some shoes to fill now, Captain.
vidsubtitles_youfamiliarwiththeai: ^2Salter: ^7You familiar with the air intercept systems, Ethan?
vidsubtitles_youchangedthecourseo: ^2Admiral Coupe: ^7You changed the course of the war, Commander Reyes. Because of you, our fleet's back online. STRATCOM is very proud of your actions.
vidsubtitles_yessirwhoelseknowsab: ^2Reyes: ^7Yes, sir. Who else knows about this?
vidsubtitles_yesmaamivelocatedone: ^2Ethan: ^7Yes, ma'am. I've located one with drop capabilities.
vidsubtitles_yeahwelljustremember: ^2Gator: ^7Yeah, well, just remember, I control the well deck from up here. Those plasmaspheric winds get awful tough if you’re ‘inadvertently’ locked out.
vidsubtitles_yeahsilverliningarou: ^2Omar: ^7Yeah. Silver lining around that reticle is SetDef didn't ask permission then, and we're not asking permission now.
vidsubtitles_wouldyouhaveleftmeou: ^2Reyes: ^7Would you have left me out there?
vidsubtitles_withalltheloveinmyhe: ^2MaCallum: ^7With all the love in my heart, Mom.
vidsubtitles_wildeastninthcentury: ^2Griff: ^7Wild East. Ninth century China, Tang dynasty. Invention of gunpowder. That’s where I belong.
vidsubtitles_wholefleethereingene: ^2Salter: ^7Whole fleet here in Geneva, doesn't seem right.
vidsubtitles_whatsourplanofattack: ^2Brooks: ^7What’s our plan of attack when we get to the top?
vidsubtitles_whatdoyouneedfrommel: ^2Ferran: ^7What do you need from me, Lieutenant?
vidsubtitles_whatdidyougetonthere: ^2Reyes: ^7What did you get on the report?
vidsubtitles_wewillreportthelates: ^2Reporter: ^7We will report the latest developments as details become available.
vidsubtitles_weweresetuponvestath: ^2Salter: ^7We were set up on Vesta. They knew the Tigris or Ret would respond.
vidsubtitles_wevesufferedunthinka: ^2Raines: ^7We’ve suffered unthinkable casualties today. Captain Alder, Captain Ferran-
vidsubtitles_wevegotlimitedbootsa: ^2Reyes: ^7We've got limited boots and guns. Lieutenant Salter and I will deploy with you.
vidsubtitles_wetakeretoutoftheequ: ^2Reyes: ^7We take Ret out of the equation. She’s seen enough.
vidsubtitles_westaytrenchedinhere: ^2Salter: ^7We stay trenched in down here, we're sitting ducks.
vidsubtitles_weshouldnthavebeendo: ^2Salter: ^7We shouldn't have been down there in the first place…
vidsubtitles_weshouldfindaplaceto: ^2Reyes: ^7We should find a place to land.
vidsubtitles_weshouldcontactadmir: ^2Gator: ^7We should contact Admiral Raines now, Commander.
vidsubtitles_weregonnaturnthetabl: ^2Reyes: ^7We’re gonna turn the tables. Set up an ambush of our own back home.
vidsubtitles_weregoindowntheresea: ^2Reyes: ^7We’re goin’ down there. Search and rescue.
vidsubtitles_wereceivedanemergenc: ^2Gator: ^7We received an emergency OPREP captain, what's your ETA?
vidsubtitles_weneedtoactonthisint: ^2Raines: ^7We need to act on this intel, Captain.
vidsubtitles_weluretheolympustoge: ^2Reyes: ^7We lure the Olympus to Geneva, and take it out.
vidsubtitles_wellusetheirownshipa: ^2Reyes: ^7We'll use their own ship against them and launch a full assault from the Olympus bridge.
vidsubtitles_welliguessillseeyoub: ^2Salter: ^7Well, I guess I'll see you both in hell.
vidsubtitles_wellhavetofightourwa: ^2Brooks: ^7We'll have to fight our way on.
vidsubtitles_wellgowithoutitthats: ^2Omar: ^7We'll go without it. That's how we do things in the infantry, Lieutenant.
vidsubtitles_wellbailoutoverthepo: ^2Reyes: ^7We’ll bail out over the port side bow and zero-g to the bridge.
vidsubtitles_wellasthisletterwill: ^2MaCallum: ^7Well, as this letter will only be used in the event of my death, it may seem somewhat sorrowful, but I don’t want you to see it that way, okay? I have always felt that our stay on Earth, the time we call “life”, it's a temporary gift to be spent in service of something greater than ourselves. Death comes to us all. It is not to be feared.
vidsubtitles_wejustneedsdftothink: ^2Salter: ^7We just need SDF to think they are. They’ll be caught off guard. AATIS will engage their fleet.
vidsubtitles_wehaveinteltheenemyi: ^2Admiral Coupe: ^7We have intel the enemy is planning a surge. Time frame is unknonw but I need you back out there right away.
vidsubtitles_wehaveaccesstoansdft: ^2Reyes: ^7We have access to an SDF transponder. It was planted in the operative who took out the AATIS in Geneva.
vidsubtitles_webelieveriahsmissio: ^2Raines: ^7We believe Riah's mission was to incinerate himself along with the AATIS.
vidsubtitles_weareafraternityoftw: ^2Ferran: ^7We are a fraternity of two, you and I. A fifty percent attrition rate is not gonna fly.
vidsubtitles_warhasnofriendsreyes: ^2Ferran: ^7War has no friends, Reyes. Perhaps my motivations were selfish, but I have no intention of fighting out here alone.
vidsubtitles_vesta3wasnttheonlymi: ^2Reyes: ^7Vesta 3 wasn't the only mining colony hit by the Olympus. Collateral left a huge cache of precious metals drifting near the Sun. Those resources are UNSA property. SetDef’s got Skelters guarding a salvage team – Let’s scramble air and claim what’s ours.
vidsubtitles_vengeancethisisraven: ^2Raven-6: ^7Vengeance, this is Raven Six, we're on final approach.
vidsubtitles_underthecircumstance: ^2Ferran: ^7Under the circumstances he deemed the recovery too risky.
vidsubtitles_understoodcommanderi: ^2Jackal Pilot: ^7Understood, Commander. I’ll ram the gun-site.
vidsubtitles_understoodadmiraltig: ^2Ferran: ^7Understood Admiral. Tigris is prepared for tasking.
vidsubtitles_unclearhelmetcamstop: ^2Raines: ^7Unclear. Helmet cam stopped transmitting. It’s been 18 hours, no contact, SetDef’s made no demands.
vidsubtitles_twosecondssaltallhen: ^2Reyes: ^7Two seconds, Salt. All he needed was two more seconds.
vidsubtitles_towhomitmayconcernil: ^2Ferran: ^7To whom it may concern, I lead sailors and troops, I protect them, and sooner or later, I prepare to send them into the jaws of a hell that is the bloodiest, dirtiest, most vicious kind of warfare man has been able to devise.
vidsubtitles_topcatthisis11convoy: ^2Reyes: ^7Top Cat, this is 1-1. Convoy is down. I say again, Echo is down! Route is compromised.
vidsubtitles_tomydearestwifesarah: ^2Omar: ^7To my dearest wife Sarah, my son Noah, and my daughter, Abby, If you are reading this, I can tell you with the utmost confidence, that I died for something right and just. The cost of war is higher than any one life, and I happily give mine in defense of my men and family.
vidsubtitles_todefendittheretribu: ^2Omar: ^7To defend it, the Retribution will insert two teams. Alpha's and Bravo's. 1's and 2's.
vidsubtitles_todaywasoneofthewors: ^2Ethan: ^7Today was one of the worst days in history, and forgive me for saying it- but it was the greatest day of my life. I did everything I was trained for, and more. Together, we fought the good fight.
vidsubtitles_todaythesdfisawarmac: ^2Reyes: ^7Today, the SDF is a war machine, ruled by its military. If a leader united that force…
vidsubtitles_todaysattackwasnotli: ^2Raines: ^7Today's attack was not limited to Geneva.
vidsubtitles_thissonofabitchisaha: ^2Auguste: ^7This son of a bitch is a handful, sir. Sooner he’s under sedation the better.
vidsubtitles_thisisvesta3miningco: ^2Salter: ^7This is Vesta-3. Mining colony, provides us with raw materials we need to rebuild the fleet.
vidsubtitles_thisisthenavyibeliev: ^2Reyes: ^7This is the Navy, I believe the proper term is "blue nosing". May I continue?
vidsubtitles_thisispeterbryantrep: ^2Reporter: ^7This is Peter Bryant reporting from Geneva.
vidsubtitles_thisisnotadrilldiver: ^2Raines: ^7This is not a drill! Divert and deploy all available assets immediately!
vidsubtitles_thisisgeromedaviesfo: ^2Reporter: ^7This is Gerome Davies for IW news.
vidsubtitles_thisiscaptainsalenko: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7This is Admiral Salen Kotch of the Olympus Mons. The UNSA ship Tigris lies in ruin. There will be no rest for the enemies of The Front.
vidsubtitles_thisisanupdateonthea: ^2Raines: ^7This is an update on the AATIS gun saboteur.
vidsubtitles_thisisagroundassault: ^2Omar: ^7This is a ground assault. Captain's place is on the bridge.
vidsubtitles_thisisadmiralsalenko_1: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7This is Admiral Salen Kotch of the Olympus Mons. All SATO forces are ordered to surrender for immediate execution.
vidsubtitles_thisisadmiralsalenko: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7This is Admiral Salen Kotch of the Olympus Mons.
vidsubtitles_thisisadeliberateact: ^2Reyes: ^7This is a deliberate act of aggression, Admiral. We should be out there on patrol, not down here throwing confetti.
vidsubtitles_thisisaclassifiedbri_1: ^2Raines: ^7This is a classified briefing regarding the POW known as Riah.
vidsubtitles_thisisaclassifiedbri: ^2Raines: ^7This is a classified briefing regarding the POW apprehended in Geneva.
vidsubtitles_thisdaysnotendingany: ^2Reyes: ^7This day's not ending anytime soon. Let's keep the barrel side out, fight the enemy, not each other. You got the greenlight to do whatever it takes.
vidsubtitles_thiscouldturnthetide: ^2Brooks: ^7This could turn the tide of the war, Captain.
vidsubtitles_theywouldmobilizeand: ^2Reyes: ^7…They would mobilize, and try to take our homeland.
vidsubtitles_theywereherelessthan: ^2Griff: ^7They were here less than 5 minutes. They took a cursory glance at the inventory and I adjusted their triggers to a five pound pull. They gave me a hat.
vidsubtitles_theyusetheirfleettob: ^2Reyes: ^7They use their fleet to block us from raw materials we need to survive. Their mission is to erase everything Earth born.
vidsubtitles_theyrepoliticiansrey: ^2Raines: ^7They’re politicians, Reyes. They’ll wipe hell’s ass with whatever flag keeps the smokestacks burning. To these men, the idea of mounting an offensive triggers a fresh and unplanned piss. Until there’s war, the warriors aren’t in charge.
vidsubtitles_theyarentrevolutiona: ^2Reyes: ^7They aren’t revolutionaries. They want absolute power. They raid colonies, take resources, and control territories by force.
vidsubtitles_theyareneverafraidth: ^2Ferran: ^7They are never afraid, they never complain, and they spend all of their time trying to think of ways to help one another achieve victory and save us all from certain death. It is selflessness beyond the pale. My dedication to them, stands above all else, save for the freedom of our world.
vidsubtitles_theyappeartobetracki: ^2Ethan: ^7They appear to be tracking our fleet.
vidsubtitles_theunsafleetisfinish: ^2SDF Operative: ^7The UNSA fleet is finished. Moving to AATIS system destruct now.
vidsubtitles_thestrengthofthepack: ^2MaCallum: ^7Look, the strength of the pack is in all the wolves, Captain. All in, no matter the cost. They were ready. Now, if you don't have the will to make that kind of choice, then like me, you have no place being in command.
vidsubtitles_theshowmustgoonidfee: ^2Reyes: ^7The show must go on. I’d feel better if we were on patrol.
vidsubtitles_theshipwontfirecapta: ^2Kloos: ^7The ship won't fire, Captain. The weapons system's not enabled.
vidsubtitles_thesettlementdefense: ^2Reyes: ^7The Settlement Defense Front built an army and broke away from the Earth with blood and violence.
vidsubtitles_thesesdfvesselsarein: ^2Ethan: ^7These SDF vessels are in dry dock, sir. They’re being built, repaired or resupplied.
vidsubtitles_thesecretmissioniund: ^2MaCallum: ^7But the secret mission I undertook every single day, was to protect the two of you from anyone, or anything, that threatened your health and well being. So promise me you will take care of one another, and, please, live your lives to the fullest.
vidsubtitles_therewasnothingyouco: ^2Brooks: ^7There was nothing you could do, Captain!
vidsubtitles_theresalonedestroyer: ^2Reyes: ^7There’s a lone destroyer in an asteroid field orbiting Europa. They’re moving in to block our access to the water. Right now that ship is alone. This should be a fast win. We locate the Solis, and disable it.
vidsubtitles_therearethreeantiair: ^2Reyes: ^7There are three Anti-Air guns that need to be taken out before our birds can move in and provide support.
vidsubtitles_theofficerscommitmen: ^2Admiral Coupe: ^7The officers commitment exhibited the highest traditions of Naval Service.
vidsubtitles_thenuclearoptionwith: ^2Gator: ^7The nuclear option with a pony tail.
vidsubtitles_thenewfrontieroffere: ^2Reyes: ^7The new frontier offered the promise of a new beginning…
vidsubtitles_theneedsofourplanetw: ^2Reyes: ^7The needs of our planet were greater than she could supply.
vidsubtitles_thenavyimbuedmetoacc: ^2Gibson: ^7The Navy imbued me to accomplish the mission and never quit. To that end, I’ll never stop loving you no matter where, or when, I go.
vidsubtitles_theinternaldrivethat: ^2Gibson: ^7The internal drive that earned me my rank, cost me a marriage.
vidsubtitles_theintelyouvebeenget: ^2Salter: ^7The intel you’ve been getting from the Admiral.
vidsubtitles_thefronthavebeensalv: ^2Reyes: ^7The Front have been salvaging parts from a scrapyard outside Pluto. They have one Destroyer and a small Skelter squadron on station. We deploy now, we can hit the ships and commandeer that salvage. We need all the scrap we can get.
vidsubtitles_thefrontdestroyedour: ^2Reyes: ^7The Front destroyed our fleet. Let's do the same to them.
vidsubtitles_thefacilitystoastlet: ^2Salter: ^7The facility's toast. Let's get back to base and report to Raines.
vidsubtitles_thatsnotmynamethatis: ^2Riah: ^7That’s not my name. That is the moniker of an Earthen fool.
vidsubtitles_thatsfordamnsurecant: ^2Reyes: ^7That's for damn sure. Can’t argue with that.
vidsubtitles_thatschiefbryantling: ^2Ferran: ^7That's Chief Bryant Ling. He's a Tigris corpsman.
vidsubtitles_thatsashamehewasagoo: ^2Raines: ^7That’s a shame. He was a good man. A good Marine.
vidsubtitles_thatfacilityisablack: ^2Reyes: ^7That facility is a black site, Admiral. Why the hell is SetDef allowed in that airspace?
vidsubtitles_thankyoubeingtogethe:
^2Gibson: ^7Thank you. Being together was a gift.
With love always,
Laura
vidsubtitles_thankyouaspartofthea: ^2Reyes: ^7Thank you. As part of the Admiral’s progressive command decree, our evaluation process includes an interview to be filed by a squad mate of lateral rank. In this case, that’s yours truly.
vidsubtitles_thanksforhelpingbrin:
^2Griff: ^7Thanks for helping bring me into this world. I did my best to be a good man.
Maynard Griffin.
vidsubtitles_thankschiefletsgetba: ^2Reyes: ^7Thanks, Chief. Let's get back to work.
vidsubtitles_tellauntjoyceisaidhi: ^2Kashima: ^7Tell Aunt Joyce I said hi and I love her, and give Baily a big kiss and a new tennis ball for me. Everyone here has a mother and father, but you and dad only have one son. So I'm sorry I didn't make it back.
vidsubtitles_surecomeandseeusmore: ^2Gator: ^7Sure. Come and see us more often.
vidsubtitles_stratcomsendsusoutwe: ^2Reyes: ^7STRATCOM sends us out, we get hit. This time it was Tigris, next time it's Ret. All respect to the Admiral, the desk is not the deck. It’s time to raise the black flag and start cutting throats.
vidsubtitles_stratcomiswellawareo: ^2Raines: ^7STRATCOM is well aware of our grievances. At this time, no use of force is being considered on the operational level. These are the laws of war, son.
vidsubtitles_stratcomhasintelthat: ^2Reyes: ^7STRATCOM has intel that an SDF leadership conference is scheduled in the Kuiper belt. Four destroyers are meeting to transfer HVTs to the “Icarius.” We’ll get ourselves aboard and take out the HVTs. This one’s just you and me, Salt. Full stealth.
vidsubtitles_stratcomcanonlyassum: ^2Raines: ^7STRATCOM can only assume an invasion would follow.
vidsubtitles_staffsergeantomarsai: ^2Reyes: ^7Staff Sergeant Omar said to pick your mission, don’t let it pick you. That’s exactly what we’re gonna do.
vidsubtitles_staffsergeantomarkia: ^2Reyes: ^7-Staff Sergeant Omar. KIA on Vesta-3 sir.
vidsubtitles_springspinscoilsinno: ^2Griff : ^7Springs, pins, coils. Innocuous by themselves, but put them in their proper place and you got something powerful and precise. That ain’t sheep.
vidsubtitles_spottedbyadefensespe: ^2Gator : ^7Spotted by a defense spectroscope, deep field scan. It’s gigantic.
vidsubtitles_sowewouldvelostourgu: ^2MaCallum: ^7So we would've lost our guns, they would have lost their transponder signal.
vidsubtitles_sowewentbeyondtherea: ^2Reyes: ^7So we went beyond the reaches of our atmosphere.
vidsubtitles_sowestandbywithourba: ^2Reyes: ^7So we stand by with our barrels in the sand and watch a fleet week parade?
vidsubtitles_sotowhatdoiowetheple: ^2Gator: ^7So, to what do I owe the pleasure?
vidsubtitles_sonofabitchthisfleet: ^2Salter: ^7Son of a bitch. This fleet sh...stuff is nonsense. We should be up in our jackals flying watch.
vidsubtitles_smartbastardhowmanyy: ^2Reyes: ^7Smart bastard. How many did you get?
vidsubtitles_siryoureourleadernot: ^2MaCallum: ^7You're our leader, sir. Not our savior.
vidsubtitles_sirweregettingstitch: ^2Brooks: ^7Sir, we're getting stitched up over here! No time to waste!
vidsubtitles_sirwerebehindenemyli: ^2Ethan: ^7Sir, we’re behind enemy lines now, in the heat of battle. Time is short. You’ve given an order from which there is likely no return. You did what had to be done. All in. I’m proud of you. You’re a born leader, sir.
vidsubtitles_sirthatobjectiverequ: ^2Reyes: ^7Sir, that objective required a full strike force, not a four man team.
vidsubtitles_sirimnotquitesurehow: ^2Griff: ^7Sir, I’m not quite sure how a son greets his father after not seeing him for a lifetime. Guess I’ll say, "Hi, dad."
vidsubtitles_siradmiralrainesison: ^2Comms Officer: ^7Sir, Admiral Raines is on the line.
vidsubtitles_shuttlebrookstakethe: ^2Salter: ^7Shuttle. Brooks, take them out. Ethan, with me.
vidsubtitles_shouldstillbesuperso: ^2Brooks: ^7Should still be supersonic at nine hundred.
vidsubtitles_shesrightoutthereina: ^2Ferran: ^7She's right out there. In all her guts and glory.
vidsubtitles_settlementdefensefro: ^2Reyes: ^7Settlement Defense Front doesn’t make demands. They planted a flag on our rock. They executed three men and shot down a pilot.
vidsubtitles_setdeflaunchedaconcu: ^2Raines: ^7SetDef launched a concurrent strike on the Moon Gateway Port.
vidsubtitles_setdefhellasisinvenu: ^2Reyes: ^7SetDef Hellas is in Venus atmosphere repairing attack damage. Intel reports it’s carrying chemical weapons. SCARs and Marines will board for search and destroy. We’ll locate the chem-munitions and take out the carrier.
vidsubtitles_setdefdestroyersenga: ^2Reyes: ^7SetDef destroyers engaged a critical Port Operations outpost. A squadron of friendlies is defending, but they need reinforcement. Let’s deploy and disable those destroyers. We lose that outpost, we can’t get resources into our Lunar port.
vidsubtitles_sdfscoutshipcamethro: ^2Salter: ^7SDF scout ship came through. We shot it down.
vidsubtitles_sdfmovesinouraatisgu: ^2Raines: ^7The rules of engagement prohibit definitive action under these circumstances.
vidsubtitles_sdfisguardingtargets: ^2Reyes: ^7SDF is guarding targets of opportunity, out here.
vidsubtitles_sdfgalaxiusisholding: ^2Reyes: ^7SDF Galaxius is holding a weapon they poached off Europa. They’ve got kidnapped engineers on board to help replicate it. Best efforts to rescue the engineers but weapon retrieval is primary.
vidsubtitles_sdfcarriercerberusis: ^2Reyes: ^7SDF carrier Cerberus is dry docked for resupply in the Miranda moon asteroid field. Payload says there’s a prototype airship in the hangar. Let’s mount an infil, commandeer the prototype and keep it out of the fight.
vidsubtitles_sdfajaksarerefueling: ^2Reyes: ^7SDF Ajaks are refueling on the surface of Titan. After the air battle with Olympus Mons, they won’t expect us back there. Element of surprise is on our side. Let’s move in for a strike.
vidsubtitles_saturnsmoontitanitsh: ^2Raines: ^7Saturn’s moon, Titan. It’s home to a critical SDF fueling station.
vidsubtitles_satoscarteamunitshav: ^2Reporter: ^7SATO SCAR team units have recaptured top-secret SATO tech, stolen mere hours before today’s vicious attack on Geneva.
vidsubtitles_satoofficialshavenot: ^2Reporter: ^7SATO officials have not responded to questions regarding the nature of the weaponry retrieved, nor is there word on the fate of the allied engineers reportedly kidnapped from the UNSA site where the SATO tech in question was stored.
vidsubtitles_satoforceshavepreven: ^2Reporter: ^7SATO forces have prevented a chemical attack on Earth, destroying a Settlement Defense Front ship carrying the payload.
vidsubtitles_satoforcesbackedbysc: ^2Reporter: ^7SATO forces backed by SCAR-led airstrikes, have destroyed the Settlement Defense Front’s primary fueling station on Titan, Saturn’s largest moon.
vidsubtitles_satoforcesaretrenche: ^2Salter: ^7SATO Forces are trenched in outside setting up a FOB.
vidsubtitles_sarahpleasekeepourba: ^2Omar: ^7Sarah, please keep our babies safe and find it in your heart to forgive me for leaving you alone. If my last breath is not in the battlefield, then surely it will be in your arms. Keep me in your hearts, always.
vidsubtitles_salvagedwhatwecouldf: ^2Salter: ^7Salvaged what we could from the Ret. Comms are up.
vidsubtitles_saltgetacombatrescue: ^2Reyes: ^7Salt, get a combat rescue team out there now.
vidsubtitles_rogersixyoureclearto: ^2Vengeance: ^7Copy, Six. Vengeance is awaiting your arrival.
vidsubtitles_rogerinboundforgunru: ^2Jackal Pilot: ^7Roger. Inbound for gun run. Time to target: ten seconds.
vidsubtitles_rightnowjointstrateg: ^2Raines: ^7Right now, Joint Strategic Air Command, and you.
vidsubtitles_reyesweretakingcasua: ^2Salter: ^7Reyes, we're taking casualties here. Running out of time!
vidsubtitles_reyesgetthehelloutof: ^2Salter: ^7Reyes, get the hell out of there!
vidsubtitles_responsetimefromthat: ^2Gator: ^7Response time from that distance would be considerable. We couldn’t render aid.
vidsubtitles_reportstonightofauns: ^2Reporter: ^7Reports tonight of a UNSA victory against the Settlement Defense Front.
vidsubtitles_relievethebottakethe: ^2Raines: ^7Relieve the bot, take the prisoner into custody.
vidsubtitles_ravenflighttogrounds: ^2Salter: ^7Raven flight to ground, SCAR 1-2, requesting re-entry.
vidsubtitles_rainesforbidmesendin: ^2Salter: ^7Raines forbid me sending assets in. He didn’t forbid you. Find him Ferran.
vidsubtitles_raiderwereduginwitht: ^2Salter: ^7Raider, we're dug in with the Marines. Taking fire!
vidsubtitles_raideritsfeverifyouc: ^2Salter: ^7Raider, it's Fever. If you can hear me, cut us loose and get our guns up.
vidsubtitles_proximitytothesunisa: ^2Reyes: ^7Proximity to the sun is a risk. Our Jacks can only take that heat for a matter of minutes. Let’s get out and back on a tight loop.
vidsubtitles_privatestepbackstepb: ^2Brooks: ^7Private! Step back! Step back, step back!
vidsubtitles_prideisonehundredper: ^2Omar: ^7Pride is one-hundred percent bona-fide bull shit, Reyes. You just make sure the mission comes first.
vidsubtitles_prepareyourmengetast: ^2Reyes: ^7Prepare your men. Get a strike package up.
vidsubtitles_pettyofficergetthata: ^2Raines: ^7Petty Officer, get that AATIS back up. We still got enemy ships in our airspace.
vidsubtitles_overtitanyousaidwewe: ^2Ethan: ^7Over Titan, you said we were brothers. I always wanted to know what a family really is. Now, I do.
vidsubtitles_overagrainypicturefa: ^2Gator: ^7Over a grainy picture? Fat chance. They didn’t cancel evolution over the Loch Ness Monster. Lots of confetti and tons of pride tied up in this thing.
vidsubtitles_ourteamwassenttosecu: ^2Raines: ^7Our team was sent to secure classified weapons from a closed facility.
vidsubtitles_ourteamhascompleteda: ^2Raines: ^7Our team has completed a forensic evaluation of the SDF asset we now know as Riah.
vidsubtitles_ourprimaryobjectivei_1: ^2Omar: ^7Our primary objective is to retake that port.
vidsubtitles_ourprimaryobjectivei: ^2Reyes: ^7Our primary objective is infiltrating the orbital platform.  Flying directly up to the shipyard is a no-go due to their active intercept system so this a ground assault.
vidsubtitles_ourenterprisingrussi: ^2Griff: ^7Our enterprising Russian brethren did a little import export deal with their Canadian friends. “Exhibition hockey game-slash-Military surplus sale.”
vidsubtitles_ourcourseofactionmov: ^2Raines: ^7Our course of action moving forward is to buy Earth time, while we rebuild our fleet.
vidsubtitles_ourc12andassaultvehi: ^2Salter: ^7Our C12 and assault vehicles are down. Without the ordnance they were carrying, we need to run an air-strike to take out the tower. MaCallum designated a gas venting turbine. We hit it, the pressure builds and the tower detonates. Ready to party?
vidsubtitles_onlythenavywouldbuil: ^2Omar: ^7Yeah. Only the Navy could build a ship designed to sink.
vidsubtitles_onlyifyourefullbore: ^2Kashima: ^7Yeah, but only if you're full bore.
vidsubtitles_oneofthemanysignsiwa: ^2Griff: ^7One of the many signs I was born too late.
vidsubtitles_onceigetyourhardcopy: ^2Admiral Coupe: ^7Once I get your hard copy signature on this we'll get it filed.
vidsubtitles_onceaboardwellshutdo: ^2Salter: ^7Once aboard, we’ll shut down the bridge and aft combat systems.
vidsubtitles_okyoureadytofacethem: ^2Reyes: ^7Ok, you ready to face the music?
vidsubtitles_nowtoroundyououtther_1: ^2Griff: ^7Now, to round you out, there's equipment.
vidsubtitles_nowtoroundyououtther: ^2Griff: ^7Now, to round you out, there's equipment.
vidsubtitles_nopopsdadwasatankfar: ^2Omar: ^7No. Pops. Dad was a tank farmer. Worked the pipelines for about thirty years. Retired just before the SDF took it over.
vidsubtitles_noonesgoinghomeyoubo: ^2Reyes: ^7No one's going home. You board that ship and you terminate this place, Salt. Do as much damage as you can before SDF takes you out.
vidsubtitles_noonesevercollidedwi: ^2Gator : ^7No one’s ever collided with the sky. Granted, Retribution handles like a brick in the bay, but I got the old girl dialed in.
vidsubtitles_nomarineseverbeenthi: ^2Omar: ^7No Marine’s ever been this close to the daystar, that’s for sure.
vidsubtitles_noblebuttheshipyardr: ^2MaCallum: ^7And that's noble, but the shipyard remains intact.
vidsubtitles_noahbeanhonestmankee: ^2Omar: ^7Noah, be an honest man. Keep your word. Only use violence as a last resort. You're the man of the house now.
vidsubtitles_nissrinehellosweethe: ^2Gator: ^7Nissrine. Hello, sweetheart. I left for this tour before you were born. I’m sorry I won’t be able to see you grow up. Daddy wanted to make the world a better place. That’s why we made you.
vidsubtitles_newrulesnewambitions: ^2Reyes: ^7New rules, new ambitions, a new enemy.
vidsubtitles_negativetodayretribu: ^2Reyes: ^7Negative. Today, Retribution isn't a warship, it’s a parade float.
vidsubtitles_negative25isweaponsd: ^2Jackal Pilot: ^7Negative. 2-5 is weapons dry. I got nothing left, sir.
vidsubtitles_navycreedhasthewordp: ^2Reyes: ^7I'm sure the Sergeant is well aware that the word "proud" is right in the Navy creed?
vidsubtitles_mytimewascutshortbut: ^2Gator: ^7My time was cut short, but I had countless blessings. I married the perfect woman. I have a brand new daughter on the way. I’d be selfish to ask for more.
vidsubtitles_mymomsandypassedaway: ^2Griff: ^7My mom, Sandy, passed away this year. I went back to the old house just before shipping out and found a box with your silver star for Valor. My mom kept it all this time.
vidsubtitles_myguyseyesonmeasfara: ^2Omar: ^7My guys, eyes on me. As far as Ethan goes- I will personally vouch for this stiff metal motherfucker. He’s one of us.
vidsubtitles_musteronthewelldecki: ^2Reyes: ^7Muster on the Well Deck in five, Staff Sergeant.
vidsubtitles_musterinfiveonthefli: ^2Omar: ^7Muster in five on the flight deck.
vidsubtitles_multiplecasualtiesfr: ^2Gator: ^7Multiple casualties from the crash maneuver, sir.
vidsubtitles_missioncomesfirstoma: ^2Salter: ^7Mission comes first. Omar's words, not mine.
vidsubtitles_michaelaaronpagemech: ^2Reyes: ^7“Michael Aaron Page”. Mechanical engineering department, two years.
vidsubtitles_mechanizedbotsguardt: ^2Salter: ^7Mechanized. Bots guard the facility. Our mission is to assess what happened, and report back to the Admiral immediately.
vidsubtitles_martathenavyhasmadem: ^2Yetide: ^7Marta, the Navy has made my life a long distance love affair. The things I love are all far away. My home, my animals…You. I am doing important work. I’m ready for anything. Even this. The military did not take my life. I volunteered it.
vidsubtitles_marinestakepointyour: ^2Omar: ^7Marines take point. You ride in with us, see how the view changes.
vidsubtitles_macmakesurepowersupt: ^2Reyes: ^7Mac, make sure power’s up to snuff.
vidsubtitles_ltreyesimpromotingyo: ^2Raines: ^7Lt. Reyes- I'm promoting you to the rank of Commander. You are now the acting Captain of Retribution.
vidsubtitles_lockstepmarchingdres: ^2Griff: ^7Lockstep marching, dressing alike and following the rule. A little structure and group mentality can soothe the soul, Lieutenant.
vidsubtitles_listenupthefrontisun: ^2Reyes: ^7Listen up. The Front is unaware we control the Olympus. We're going to Mars.
vidsubtitles_liftplatformtotheshi: ^2MaCallum: ^7Lift platform to the shipyard is 100 klicks north-north east. We're in the middle of nowhere out here.
vidsubtitles_lieutenantsaltershea: ^2Ferran: ^7Lieutenant Salter. She asked the admiral for a retrieval team.
vidsubtitles_lieutenantreyeswenee: ^2Gator: ^7Lieutenant Reyes, we need you up here, right away. Bridge out.
vidsubtitles_lieutenantreyesiimpl: ^2Raines: ^7Lieutenant Reyes, I implore you to use diplomacy in this office. Take a different tact.
vidsubtitles_lieutenantmakenomist: ^2Raines: ^7Lieutenant Reyes, make no mistake, my instincts, which are aligned indelibly with your own, are that we need to engage.
vidsubtitles_letskeepthisoffradar: ^2Ferran: ^7Let’s keep this off radar. I'll have a SITREP for you shortly. Actual, out.
vidsubtitles_letsgotoworkcaptainr: ^2Ferran: ^7Let's go to work Captain Reyes. Stay sharp out there. All of you.
vidsubtitles_letsgetoutthereandfi: ^2Reyes: ^7Let’s get out there and fight for them.
vidsubtitles_letsgetalookatthisso: ^2Reyes: ^7Let’s get a look at this son of a bitch.
vidsubtitles_letsgetalookattheday: ^2Reyes: ^7Let's get a look at the day side.
vidsubtitles_letsbringethanwithus: ^2Omar: ^7Let's bring Ethan with us. I want him on the team.
vidsubtitles_letmemakeoursituatio: ^2Raines: ^7Let me make our situation absolutely clear. We are now at war with the Settlement Defense Front.
vidsubtitles_keepmeinyourprayersa: ^2Gator: ^7Keep me in your prayers and try to do one good deed every day.
vidsubtitles_jointoperationyouand: ^2Omar: ^7Joint operation. You and me. How copy?
vidsubtitles_jackpotallstationsis: ^2Reyes: ^7Jackpot. All stations, I say again Jackpot.
vidsubtitles_jackalsareweaponsloo: ^2Jackal Pilot: ^7Jackals are weapons loose, danger close.
vidsubtitles_iwishidknownyoustill: ^2Griff: ^7I wish I’d known you still lived in Tennessee. I would have dropped by. We could’ve had a beer and caught up. I forgive you for leaving.  I hope you’re not mad at me for writing.
vidsubtitles_iwillkeepyoupostedon: ^2Raines: ^7I will keep you posted on any and all developments. Top Cat out.
vidsubtitles_iwantyoutoknowifollo: ^2Griff: ^7I want you to know I followed in your footsteps. I joined the Navy. Thought it would make you proud and if we ever saw each other we’d have more to talk about. I went to sniper school to be sharpshooter but my vision changed and I became an instructor. I’m currently deployed aboard the UNSA carrier Retribution.
vidsubtitles_iveuploadedthetitand: ^2Raines: ^7I’ve uploaded the Titan dossier. Direct your attention to the CIC, Captain.
vidsubtitles_ivegottenyearsontheb: ^2Salter: ^7I've got ten years on the books with that loyal bastard. He saved my ass more time than I can count. I can’t do this without him.
vidsubtitles_ivebeeninformedstrat: ^2Raines: ^7I’ve been informed, STRATCOM has approved your initiative in Geneva.
vidsubtitles_itwasplantedintheope: ^2Reyes: ^7It was a suicide mission. It would've stopped transmitting when the operative was killed.
vidsubtitles_itwasmyhonorandprivi:
^2Ferran: ^7It was my honor and privilege to command such brave souls.

Peace to the fallen,
Captain Maureen Ferran
vidsubtitles_itsdamngoodtoseeyous: ^2Raines: ^7It's damn good to see you son.
vidsubtitles_itsatransponderemitt: ^2Raines: ^7 It's a transponder. Emitting as we speak.
vidsubtitles_ithinkofyouandmyhear: ^2Yetide: ^7I think of you and my heart races, I smile, I laugh out loud and people tell me I always seem so happy. I am. I have you.
vidsubtitles_itaskedapilotandtwos: ^2Ferran: ^7I tasked a pilot and two spotters, and we set out to your last known location.
vidsubtitles_istillamiaskedstratc: ^2Salter: ^7I still am. I asked STRATCOM to mount a rescue team. Admiral Raines refused. Wouldn’t risk five men for two.
vidsubtitles_ispeaknowtotheretrib: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7I speak now to the Retribution. We will continue to fight you inside and outside your fading world. Your cities will surrender, broken and weak. We will not fail.
vidsubtitles_iseeahangarupaheadwe: ^2Salter: ^7I see a hangar up ahead. We can set down inside, out of the sun.
vidsubtitles_ipromisedmyselfiwoul: ^2Kashima: ^7I promised myself I wouldn’t get close to people here, but it’s kind of impossible not to. I wasn’t scared here, but I was home sick. Mom, I had a dream, last night, that you were making dinner. Yes, my favorite, porkchops, and we were all at the table together.
vidsubtitles_ipitythethingyoucall: ^2Riah: ^7I pity the thing you call courage.
vidsubtitles_inthemeantimeivebrie: ^2Raines: ^7In the meantime, I've briefed Lt. Salter on developments in the field that need your attention.
vidsubtitles_interrogativetheguns: ^2Ethan: ^7Interrogative: The guns won't be down, sir.
vidsubtitles_intensefightingingen: ^2Reporter: ^7Intense fighting in Geneva has subsided, as SATO troops defend the UNSA capitol against invading Settlement Defense Forces.
vidsubtitles_inoureffortstobuytim: ^2Raines: ^7In our efforts to buy time for the fleet to rebuild, we need to hit SetDef's battle readiness.
vidsubtitles_ineededthosetwosecon: ^2Salter: ^7I needed those two seconds to get us off the X…
vidsubtitles_imthepilotofthisship: ^2Salter: ^7I'm the pilot of this ship, It's my job to make sure that we get back!
vidsubtitles_imsorrylieutenantyou: ^2Ferran: ^7I’m sorry, Lieutenant. You were following orders.
vidsubtitles_iminovermypaygradewh: ^2Griff: ^7I’m in over my pay grade when it comes to the finer points of war, Lieutenant, but I’ll be damned if we can’t find some solace in the simple beauty of a sidearm and a sixth grade teacher.
vidsubtitles_imgettingantsyiftheg: ^2Reyes: ^7I’m getting antsy. If the good Lord wanted the Navy on terra firma he’d have made the sky brown. Pilots make bad pedestrians.
vidsubtitles_iloveyouoliviayoullb: ^2Gator: ^7I Love you Olivia. Welcome our baby into this world and cherish her for me. Remind her about her daddy, and, please, never be afraid to do what you need to find happiness.
vidsubtitles_ilovedmyjobbutihated: ^2MaCallum: ^7I loved my job, but I hated war.
vidsubtitles_illprimetheordnancei: ^2Ethan: ^7I'll prime the ordnance I commandeered from the Olympus Mons to hit those AA turrets.
vidsubtitles_illpilotaraventounsa: ^2Salter: ^7I’ll pilot a Raven to UNSA-HQ. We'll make that our base of operations.
vidsubtitles_illleaveyoubegotsome: ^2Griff: ^7Well, I'll leave you be. Got some carbines to set up for you.
vidsubtitles_illdowhatevericantok: ^2Reyes: ^7I'll do whatever it takes to keep us secure.
vidsubtitles_ilikedschoolsixhours: ^2Griff: ^7I liked school. Six hours a day of regimented repetitive instruction.
vidsubtitles_iknowthisisnteasyple: ^2Yetide: ^7I know this isn’t easy. Please don’t cry for me, or us. Cry for a world that couldn’t make peace.
vidsubtitles_iknowihadwhateverywo: ^2Gibson: ^7I know I had what every woman envied, a husband that gave life more meaning. You were my handsome better half. Since the day we locked eyes, I thought of you constantly. I still do.
vidsubtitles_iknewtherewassomethi: ^2Omar: ^7I knew there was something I didn't like about you sons of bitches.
vidsubtitles_iknewitlemmeguessope: ^2Gator: ^7I knew it. Lemme guess. Operation “why the hell was the Admiral on board”? Am I right?
vidsubtitles_ikeepsingingoursongo: ^2Yetide: ^7I keep singing our song over and over, trying to remind myself that it’s going to be okay, and that I will fall asleep next to you every night when all this distance is done.
vidsubtitles_ihavefaiththiswarwil: ^2MaCallum: ^7I have faith this war will end in victory and you will remain free to pursue whatever paths you wish, free from violence and cruelty.
vidsubtitles_ihaveeverythingittak: ^2Salter: ^7I have everything it takes in spades. I understand risk, I multi-task like a mother…really well, and I take myself and the equipment to the peak of proficiency. Plus, I can beat anybody like a drum. Shit goes down, you want me up.
vidsubtitles_ifyouarereadingthisi: ^2Gator: ^7If you are reading this, I guess I didn’t make it home. I was prepared to face danger and death. I hope I did so with dignity.
vidsubtitles_iftheyresittingandim: ^2Reyes: ^7If they’re sitting and I’m standing, maybe. So what can’t you tell me that I can’t repeat?
vidsubtitles_ifinallytrackeddowny: ^2Griff: ^7I finally tracked down your address through the human resource department in Washington. I had to use my birth certificate to prove we were related.
vidsubtitles_ifallgoesasplannedth: ^2Raines: ^7If all goes as planned the SDF fleet, including the Olympus Mons, will receive the all clear signal and enter our airspace provoking a counterattack by our AATIS guns.
vidsubtitles_idonteitherinpurelym: ^2Ferran: ^7I don’t either. In purely mathematical terms, it’s a mistake to go after him. But we’ve buried 19 commanders today. I’m not losing another. Send me their last known coordinates and we’ll see what we can do.
vidsubtitles_idontbuythateitherth: ^2Gator: ^7I don’t buy that either. That’s your squadron, they look up to you.
vidsubtitles_icouldntrammyownship: ^2Reyes: ^7I couldn't ram my own ship. I would have killed them.
vidsubtitles_icandobothicanhitthe: ^2Salter: ^7I can do both. I can hit the shipyard and drop out of here.
vidsubtitles_icanalwayssicsaltero: ^2Reyes: ^7I can always sic' Salter on you.
vidsubtitles_ibringmymenhomesaltw: ^2Reyes: ^7I bring my men home, Salt, we do both!
vidsubtitles_iagreewithyoubutilld: ^2Gator: ^7I agree with you, but I’ll deny it under oath.
vidsubtitles_howdidyouaccountforr: ^2Ethan: ^7How did you account for radial velocity?
vidsubtitles_holdheregatorcallyou: ^2Reyes: ^7Hold here, Gator. Call you if I need you.
vidsubtitles_hisimplantedtranspon: ^2Raines: ^7His implanted transponder would have been destroyed, halting its signal, sending an all clear to the enemy fleet.
vidsubtitles_hindsightsatacticalm: ^2Raines: ^7Hindsight’s a tactical miscalculation we can’t afford.
vidsubtitles_highlynavybroughtint: ^2Griff: ^7Highly. Navy brought in the Bureau.  Fleet-wide inspection. Big crackdown.
vidsubtitles_heymomdadwhenijoined: ^2Kashima: ^7Hey, Mom, Dad. When I joined the Marines, I told you that I’m ready to give my life for fighting for a good cause. If I don’t come home for any reason, then that’s what happened. I hope I died doing something heroic, and in the long run, I hope that I made you proud.
vidsubtitles_hesstilldowntheresal: ^2Reyes: ^7He's still down there Salt! Turn this ship around!
vidsubtitles_hesrightthiselevator: ^2MaCallum: ^7He’s right. This elevator is the only way up from the surface.
vidsubtitles_hesitationisaholeint: ^2Salter: ^7Hesitation is a hole in the head, Reyes. We both know that. There was no other way.
vidsubtitles_hescomingtothereyoug: ^2Ferran: ^7He's coming to. There you go, sailor. Open your eyes.
vidsubtitles_hesavedhisshipandcre: ^2Salter: ^7He saved his ship and crew, Chief.
vidsubtitles_hellbegladtohearthat: ^2Reyes: ^7He'll be glad to hear that. He has enormous respect for the Marines.
vidsubtitles_heartratesstabilizin: ^2Bryant Ling: ^7Heart rate's stabilizing. Blood gas is in range.
vidsubtitles_hardcopy11donotforfe: ^2Raines: ^7Hard copy, 1-1. Do not forfeit the asset. Imperative we do not lose that transponder.
vidsubtitles_griffsouttheregoseeh: ^2Salter: ^7Griff's out there, go see him, you need a weapon.
vidsubtitles_gravitationaldragand: ^2Ferran: ^7Gravitational drag and something we've been lacking: luck. We had to pry Ethan's arms open. They'd frozen around you. Protecting his captain to the end.
vidsubtitles_gottheseimagesfromca: ^2Gator: ^7Got these images from Captain Alder this morning.
vidsubtitles_gotsomeattachmentsin_1: ^2Griff: ^7Got some attachments in stock, too. Anything catch your eye?
vidsubtitles_gotsomeattachmentsin: ^2Griff: ^7Got some attachments in stock, too. Anything catch your eye?
vidsubtitles_gotakealookforyourse: ^2Raines: ^7Go take a look for yourself. I think you’ll be quite impressed. Dismissed.
vidsubtitles_got300metersonusleng: ^2Gator: ^7Got 300 meters on us lengthwise. Maybe 50 wide. Big enemy ship. Tough to find a parking spot, that’s for sure.
vidsubtitles_goodworkmetal1touchd: ^2Reyes: ^7Good work, Metal-1. Touch down and get ready to go.
vidsubtitles_goodsepwereinscannin: ^2Salter: ^7Good sep’. We’re in scanning range in 30.
vidsubtitles_givemefiveminuteswit: ^2Salter: ^7Give me five minutes with this bastard.
vidsubtitles_getreadyreyesyourene: ^2Salter: ^7Get ready Reyes, you’re next. I’m not nice like you.
vidsubtitles_getraventransportsse: ^2Reyes: ^7Get Raven transports set for evac. I want our casualties outbound right away. Drop Officer, coordinate with engineering and get us mobile.
vidsubtitles_gatorgettheadmiralon: ^2Reyes: ^7Gator, get the Admiral on the line.
vidsubtitles_gatorcalltheflightde: ^2Reyes: ^7Gator, call the flight deck, I’ll go out there myself.
vidsubtitles_fullcompanysirtheyre: ^2Ethan: ^7Full company, sir. I mean, they're idiots, but they can fight.
vidsubtitles_frontwasalreadythere: ^2Reyes: ^7Front was already there. Took out the whole team, looted the site.
vidsubtitles_forunsaarmedforcesme: ^2Reporter: ^7For UNSA Armed Forces Media, this is Renee Syhan in New Delhi.
vidsubtitles_formydearwifeoliviaa: ^2Gator: ^7For my dear wife Olivia and my daughter Nissrine.
vidsubtitles_forgettheweaponswere: ^2Salter: ^7Forget the weapons. Let's release the moorings, key in a drop and go.
vidsubtitles_firstandforemostihav: ^2Raines: ^7First and foremost, I have a classified briefing for your eyes only. Meet me in your operations office.
vidsubtitles_firesstillburnfromth: ^2Reporter: ^7Fires still burn from the charred remains of warships, the result of a suprise attack, launched against the SATO fleet. Mandatory evacuations are underway as several small pockets of fighting are ongoing, here in the city.
vidsubtitles_firearmsalcoholtabac: ^2Griff: ^7Firearms, alcohol, tobacco. Was a time a man could buy whiskey, cigarettes and a forty-five all in the same aisle of the same store.
vidsubtitles_figuredidcomeandseeh: ^2Reyes: ^7Figured I’d come and see how the other half lives.
vidsubtitles_fightourwaytothetopg: ^2Reyes: ^7Fight our way to the top- Get ourselves a ship. Pass word.
vidsubtitles_eyesuponyourhudforas: ^2Salter: ^7Eyes up on your HUD for a sitrep.
vidsubtitles_explainsthewhiteunif: ^2Omar: ^7That explains the white uniform and the submarines.
vidsubtitles_ethanwhatsthenavysof: ^2Omar: ^7Ethan, what’s the Navy’s official policy for a gunfight?
vidsubtitles_ethansetadropcoursef: ^2Reyes: ^7Ethan, set a drop course for SetDef's Orbital Shipyard.
vidsubtitles_ethansbotswillcreate: ^2Reyes: ^7Ethan's bots will create a diversion while our Ravens insert on the edge of the platform’s perimeter.
vidsubtitles_ethanhostileforcesar: ^2Reyes: ^7Ethan, hostile forces are aboard the lieutenant's destroyer.
vidsubtitles_ethangotoengineering: ^2Reyes: ^7Ethan. Go to engineering, see Mac, get a clean bill.
vidsubtitles_ethangetourtacticals: ^2Reyes: ^7Ethan, get our tacticals on the map, prepare a brief, get it to STRATCOM right away.
vidsubtitles_echoisfivemikesoutfr: ^2Auguste: ^7Echo is five mikes out from the UNSA building. City’s evacuated so the convoy’ll move quick. We’ll RV with you and the Admiral in the Medical hall. What’s your ETA?
vidsubtitles_earthsurvivorswillli: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7Earth survivors will live at gunpoint, and breathe by permission of the Front. Mars aeternum.
vidsubtitles_earthslunargatewaypo: ^2Omar: ^7Earth's Lunar Gateway Port is currently under siege.
vidsubtitles_duetocaptainaldersus: ^2Raines: ^7Due to Captain Alder's use of force, the enemy was driven into retreat. At this time, Tigris and Retribution are the only operable ships we have.
vidsubtitles_dowhatyoudidatthegat: ^2Omar: ^7You just do what you did at the Gateway and we'll zip this place right up.
vidsubtitles_domyeyesdeceivemeori: ^2Gator: ^7Do my eyes deceive me or is there a big time Jack pilot on my bridge?
vidsubtitles_didyouknowweweregonn: ^2Salter: ^7Did you know we were gonna finish this here?
vidsubtitles_didabookreportinsixt: ^2Griff: ^7Did a book report in sixth grade, Ms. Trillscott. Meaner than a wet panther but she had other attributes. I couldn’t wait to get to class.
vidsubtitles_destroyertigrisisdoc: ^2Boats: ^7Destroyer Tigris is docking a shuttle to come aboard.
vidsubtitles_desperatetimescallfo: ^2Raines: ^7…Desperate times call for desperate measures. I commend your actions.
vidsubtitles_dearandrewitsfleetwe: ^2Gibson: ^7Dear Andrew, It’s fleet week. Warships are dry docked against the dawn sky.  I’m home, but it’s not home without you.
vidsubtitles_counterintelneedtokn: ^2Reyes: ^7Counter-intel. Need to know. Until right now.
vidsubtitles_counterdeceptionwese: ^2Reyes: ^7Counter deception. We set the table and they come to eat.
vidsubtitles_copymovingasfastasic: ^2Reyes: ^7Copy. Moving as fast as I can. Hold them off!
vidsubtitles_copycommsofficerstra: ^2Gator: ^7Copy. Comms Officer, STRATCOM, Top Cat Sovereign.
vidsubtitles_copycommanderechosup: ^2MaCallum: ^7Copy, Commander. Echo support element is inbound. They'll get you through the door.
vidsubtitles_copyaftershutdownwee: ^2Omar: ^7Copy. After shut down, we exit through the cargo bay.
vidsubtitles_copy12angleisgoodyou: ^2ATC Operator: ^7Copy, 1-2. Angle is good, you're clear. Welcome home.
vidsubtitles_commandertigrisisset: ^2Ferran: ^7Commander, Tigris is set for close air support. Notify when your Marines are staged for insert.
vidsubtitles_commandersergeantgoo: ^2Marine Guard: ^7Commander, Sergeant, good to see you guys. Right this way.
vidsubtitles_commanderreyeswhatth: ^2Raines: ^7Commander Reyes, what the hell happened out there?
vidsubtitles_commanderreyesstratc: ^2Raines: ^7Commander Reyes, STRATCOM decrypted a fleet transmission from Admiral Kotch broadcast six hours before the attack.
vidsubtitles_commanderreyescaptai: ^2Boats: ^7Commander Reyes. Captain Alder's Operations Office is now yours. Be advised, his effects are still in place.
vidsubtitles_commanderreyesandlts: ^2Admiral Coupe: ^7Commander Reyes and Lt. Salter gallantly offered their own lives and those of their crew, mobilizing at close-range against superior fire power. The operation eliminated vital numbers of enemy vessels and destroyed the Settlement Defense Front's Orbital Shipyard.
vidsubtitles_commanderakeelminria: ^2Riah: ^7Commander Akeel Min Riah, of the Settlement Defense Front.
vidsubtitles_commandcentermaamits: ^2Ethan: ^7Command center, ma'am. It's a shuttle ride that way.
vidsubtitles_cminuspurposelyusedp: ^2Griff: ^7"C minus". Purposely used pencil. Immediate grounds for detention and an extra hour with Ms. Trillscott.
vidsubtitles_clashesonthelunarsur: ^2Reporter: ^7Clashes on the Lunar surface have come to an end as SATO forces reclaim the Moon Gateway harbor from the Settlement Defense Front. The gateway complex is the Earth's primary cargo commerce and passenger terminal…
vidsubtitles_captaintigriswilldro: ^2Ferran: ^7Captain, Tigris will drop in outside the Area of Operation. Once Ret joins, we'll hold position until your Marines are ready. Good flight. Out.
vidsubtitles_captaintheywontstopu: ^2Raines: ^7Captain, they won't stop until they take our world. This may be our last stand.
vidsubtitles_captainsgoingtoneedm: ^2Ethan: ^7Captain's going to need my help to get to the command center.
vidsubtitles_captainreyesthereisn: ^1Admiral Kotch: ^7Captain Reyes. There is no hope of victory.  We will bury your brothers. We will hunt your sons. Death is no disgrace.
vidsubtitles_captainpleaseicanloo: ^2Ethan: ^7Captain, please, I can look after myself.
vidsubtitles_captainillgiveyouacc: ^2Ethan: ^7Captain, I'll give you access to a drone to designate those strike positions. Hey, should be a blast.
vidsubtitles_captainidbelyingifid: ^2Raines: ^7Captain, I'd be lying if I didn't admit I got the green eye for this one. I'd gear up and join you if I could. Top Cat out.
vidsubtitles_captaingettingthegro: ^2Griff: ^7Captain. Just getting these ground-pounders gunned up for Titan.
vidsubtitles_captainferranretribu: ^2Salter: ^7Captain Ferran. Retribution was engaged by Olympus over Titan. Commander Reyes’s Jackal was hit. Ethan was aboard. They bailed. He ordered 141 out of the battle zone. Ret was taking heavy fire. Helm spooled up and pulled the plug. We left him. No weapons, no cover.
vidsubtitles_captainferranladiesg: ^2Raines: ^7Captain Ferran. Ladies, Gentlemen. It's good to see you.
vidsubtitles_captaincanyouhearmec: ^2Ferran: ^7Captain, can you hear me? Captain Reyes?
vidsubtitles_captainbeadvisedaagu: ^2Jackal Pilot: ^7Captain, be advised, AA guns are still online!
vidsubtitles_canyouidentifyashipw: ^2Salter: ^7Can you identify a ship we can use?
vidsubtitles_bythepermissionofthe: ^2Raines: ^7By the permission of the Accords, all nations have access to free an un--
vidsubtitles_bymethesemenandwomen: ^2Ferran: ^7By me, these men and women are loved with a kind of bond that exists no other place but the military. These young warriors go for days without food or sleep. They persevere when they are sick, perform miraculous feats when they are wounded, and take death defying orders without pause.
vidsubtitles_butthedistancegavewa: ^2Reyes: ^7…but the distance gave way to a movement, with no connection to the place we call home.
vidsubtitles_butsirbythetimethere: ^2Reyes: ^7But, sir, by the time there’s war it’s too late. ‘Hesitation is a hole in the head’. You drilled that into us relentlessly in flight school. ‘Work the problem, respond’.
vidsubtitles_bureauoffirearmspaid: ^2Griff: ^7Bureau of Firearms paid us a surprise visit.
vidsubtitles_bullshityouredoingre: ^2Gator: ^7Bullshit. You’re doing recon for eight highly trained aviators who wouldn’t be caught dead poking around up here.
vidsubtitles_bothofficersawareoft: ^2Admiral Coupe: ^7…both officers, aware of the imminent danger, in spite of extensive casualties, planned and skillfully executed an attack with unwavering devotion to their duty.
vidsubtitles_boatshowcanweenablet: ^2Reyes: ^7Boats? How can we enable the payload?
vidsubtitles_bluebluecommanderrey: ^2Reyes: ^7Blue, blue! It's Commander Reyes. I've got Marines with me.
vidsubtitles_blastwavealonewouldb: ^2MaCallum: ^7Blast wave alone would be quite destructive.
vidsubtitles_betyourasslongtimeco: ^2Omar: ^7You bet your ass. This has been a long time coming.
vidsubtitles_atyourbehestthepriso: ^2Raines: ^7At your behest, the prisoner will be transported to UNSA Headquarters. A med team will remove the transponder from the subject at which point the device will be incinerated.
vidsubtitles_atthistimeitsunclear: ^2Raines: ^7At this time it's unclear if the guns can be destroyed from another location
vidsubtitles_atleast100militantsw: ^2Reporter: ^7At least 100 militants were killed in the ground-based operation to cut off enemy fueling capability in the region on this, the first day in what will no doubt be a protracted war between SetDef and the UNSA.
vidsubtitles_asyoushouldyouaborte: ^2MaCallum: ^7As you should. You aborted the mission, Captain.
vidsubtitles_astratcomspokesmanwa: ^2Reporter: ^7A STRATCOM spokesman was quoted as saying, "Our orbital defenses are intact and the fleet is holding strong, keeping the enemy on the run." For now, the battle rages on, outside the Earth’s perimeter. This is  Renee Syhan in New Delhi.
vidsubtitles_astratcomofficialsay: ^2Reporter: ^7A STRATCOM official says,  “we are standing with our UNSA allies against both traditional and ‘hybrid warfare’ aggression,“- referring to the mechanized brigades the SDF fight alongside, increasingly elevating their troop numbers to well beyond the Marine and SCAR team elements currently deployed.
vidsubtitles_asthehighestrankingo: ^2Gator: ^7As the highest ranking officer on board…
vidsubtitles_asteroidrotationsflu: ^2Salter: ^7Asteroid rotation's fluctuating. About a minute give or take.
vidsubtitles_assaultinganenemyshi: ^2Raines: ^7Assaulting an enemy ship with no reinforcements…
vidsubtitles_areyoubrownnosingrig: ^2Salter: ^7Are you brown nosing right now? You're totally brown nosing.
vidsubtitles_approx1800vestahqwen: ^2Salter: ^7Approx. 1800, Vesta-HQ went dark, all attempts to make contact have since failed.
vidsubtitles_aninternallyplantedd: ^2Raines: ^7An internally planted device was found on the prisoner.
vidsubtitles_andthosecargotermina: ^2Raines: ^7And those cargo terminals receive freight critical to rebuilding our fleet. So your mission is to retake that port.
vidsubtitles_alrightyoushouldhave: ^2Gibson: ^7Alright, you should have air now, Lieutenants.
vidsubtitles_alrightsoadmiralrain: ^2Reyes: ^7Alright, so, Admiral Raines, a man of great wisdom, has ordered us to…
vidsubtitles_alrightithinkmyworkh: ^2Reyes: ^7Alright, I think my work here is through.
vidsubtitles_allstationsshotsfire: ^2Radio Operator: ^7All stations, shots fired at the AATIS control tower, say again, SHOTS FIRED!
vidsubtitles_allcallsignsechovict: ^2Auguste: ^7All callsigns, Echo Victors in contact, taking heavy enemy fire!
vidsubtitles_ajointoperationbetwe: ^2Reporter: ^7A joint operation between Gateway Coast Guard Defense Forces and special operations groups including the Navy's elite SCAR Team and UNSA Marines forced the SetDef into a full-scale retreat.
vidsubtitles_ahyouhearthatlieuten: ^2Kashima: ^7Ah, you hear that, Lieutenant? We’re setting some sort of record.
vidsubtitles_afterusingouraatisgu: ^2Raines: ^7After using our AATIS guns against our fleet, the operative known as Riah attempted to destroy the entire AATIS system. This would have left Earth vulnerable to aerial attack.
vidsubtitles_afterthegunsaredownw: ^2Reyes: ^7After the guns are down, we push into the facility and ascend to the shipyard.
vidsubtitles_affirmativethisstrik: ^2Raines: ^7Affirmative. This strike'll keep the enemy on the defensive and away from Earth.
vidsubtitles_adropintoatmospherec: ^2Yetide: ^7A drop into atmosphere could be catastrophic.
vidsubtitles_admiralrainestoldmet:
^2Ethan: ^7Admiral Raines told me that a soldier is only as good as his last mission. If this is ours, then I can say with certainty, we were damn good, sir.
Better to burn out, than it is to rust.
vidsubtitles_admiralrainese3nisin: ^2Petty Officer: ^7Admiral Raines. E3N is in position on the roof.
vidsubtitles_actualthisisretribut: ^2Gator: ^7Actual, this is Retribution. SetDef fleet is descending, inbound.
vidsubtitles_actuallydidntknowthe: ^2Reyes: ^7Actually didn’t know the Admiral was here. We saw Captain Alder and half of STRATCOM skip a two martini breakfast to do a walk through.
vidsubtitles_acalculatedrisklieut: ^2Ferran: ^7A calculated risk, Lieutenant. I'll be returning to Tigris now. Let's get back to work.
vidsubtitles_abbyimsorryididntkee: ^2Omar: ^7Abby, I’m sorry I didn’t keep my promise when I said I was coming home. My hopes for your future, gave me the strength to protect everything we hold dear. You will always be daddy’s little girl.
vidsubtitles_aatisisworkingoverti: ^2Reyes: ^7AATIS guns are working overtime today, huh, Admiral?
vidsubtitles_aatisgunsaremomentsa: ^2Ethan: ^7AATIS guns are moments away from acquiring enemy targets, Admiral.
vidsubtitles_11tobridgewhatthehel: ^2Reyes: ^71-1 to Retribution. What the hell happened, Gator?

equipment_upgrade_foam_one: Quickly double tap ^3[{+usereload,+activate}]^7 to detonate the Foam Wall on command.
equipment_upgrade_drone_one: The maximum amount of ATADs that can be deployed at once is increased to four.
equipment_upgrade_shield_one: Upgrades the battery to improve the radar and allow for longer-lasting protection.
equipment_upgrade_hack_one: The Hacking Device is faster at hacking C6 robots and can also now lock on to and control C8 robots.
equipment_upgrade_seeker_two: Hold ^3[{+frag}]^7 when deploying the Seeker to choose the target.
equipment_upgrade_seeker_one: Quickly double tap ^3[{+usereload,+activate}]^7 to detonate the Seeker on command.
equipment_upgrade_antigrav_two: Increases the radius of the explosion.
equipment_upgrade_antigrav_one: Increases the duration of the grenade.
equipment_upgrade_shock_two: Increases the damage done to C8 robots.
equipment_upgrade_shock_one: Enemies caught in the center of the grenade take greater damage.
equipment_upgrade_frag_two: Enemies that survive the explosion will be highlighted by your visor.
equipment_upgrade_frag_one: Increases the damage done to enemy robots.
equipment_coverwall_unlock: Unlock in Retribution: Doing What Needs to be Done
equipment_nano_shot_long: Nano Shots heal broken bones and provide partial health regeneration.
equipment_helmet_long: Helmets provide greater protection against headshots.
equipment_coverwall_long: Fast deploying foam wall will create a temporary barrier against bullets and other damage.
equipment_tracking_long: Frag grenade used in zero-g that tracks the enemy.
equipment_hackingdevice_long: Advanced hacking software integrated into a soldier's helmet visor. Able to give the user full control over C6 robots.
equipment_frag_long: High-powered fragmentation grenade. Employs a 2-stage explosive that releases flammable gas before detonating.
equipment_supportdrone_long: Personal flying drone with advanced AI. Automatically fires at enemy soldiers, and possesses a grenade-destroying trophy system.
equipment_antigrav_long: Deploys an array of anti-gravity generators. Lifts enemy soldiers into the air, exposing them to gunfire.
equipment_emp_long: The Shock grenade will neutralize threats in a tight radius and stun threats in an expanded radius. Especially effective against robotic combatants.
equipment_shield_long: Suit-powered personal shield that quickly expands from the user's arm. Limits shooting ability but stops most ballistic weapons.
equipment_seeker_long: A small, deployable robot that seeks out enemies and self-destructs.
